&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/179794/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;Bun v1.3.7&lt;/a&gt; ‚Äì The popular runtime updates its JavaScriptCore engine, leading to 35% faster &lt;code&gt;async&lt;/code&gt;/&lt;code&gt;await&lt;/code&gt; and ARM64 perf improvements. It also lands a new option to generate profiling data in Markdown format for easier sharing, plus native JSON5 and JSONL parsing¬†support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
